    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't know... it feels way too convenient. like, they didn't even pause to evaluate my performance this quarter, it just happened right after that meeting. and now my whole office is basically transparent glass. it's like they want everyone to see me, but also like they want me to feel like i'm in a fishbowl. you don't think it's a way to keep me under a microscope?",
